<title>
Transfer Output Retainer Assembly Disassembly and Reassembly
</title>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70A3306003">Transfer Dismounting and Remounting</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70A3306004">Transfer Assembly Components</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<intxrefpoff refid = "AENAP70A3306005">Transfer Assembly Disassembly and Reassembly</intxrefpoff>
</ptxt>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70A3306009001">
<title>
Disassembly
</title>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove transfer output flange nut while holding transfer output flange (1) using special tool.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L3C023">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09930-40113">
09930–40113
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A330023.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "50.374mm" ver = "01" gw = "139" gh = "126"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove transfer output flange (1) using special tool.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L3C024">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09913-65135">
09913–65135
</s-number>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A330024.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "61.157mm" ver = "01" gw = "116" gh = "157"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Drive out bevel pinion (1) from transfer output retainer by tapping it with plastic hammer (2).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A330025.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "53.370mm" ver = "01" gw = "146" gh = "135"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<c-change/>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Drive out front taper roller bearing (1) from bevel pinion (3) using bearing puller (2) and hydraulic press.
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I5RW0A330032.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "38.265mm" ver = "01" gw = "171" gh = "92"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove oil seal (1) using special tool.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L3C025">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09913-50121">
09913–50121
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A330026.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "52.535mm" ver = "01" gw = "146" gh = "132"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Remove rear taper roller bearing (1) and spacer (2).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A330027.jpg" width = "88.000mm" height = "47.505mm" ver = "01" gw = "200" gh = "118"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Drive out front outer race (1) and rear outer race (2) using brass bar (3).
</ptxt>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A330028.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "40.911mm" ver = "01" gw = "167" gh = "99"/>
</figure>
</s1>
</servinfosub>
<servinfosub id = "AENAP70A3306009002">
<title>
Reassembly
</title>
<attention2>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
Bevel gear and pinion must be replaced as a set when either replacement becomes necessary.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
When replacing taper roller bearing, replace as inner race and outer race assembly.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention2>
<s1>
<ptxt>
To mesh bevel gears correctly, it is prerequired to install bevel pinion to transfer output retainer properly using adjusting shim (bevel pinion shim) as follows.
</ptxt>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Install front taper roller bearing (1) to bevel pinion dummy (special tools).
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L3C026">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09922-76140">
09922–76140
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L3C027">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09922-76430">
09922–76430
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I3RH01332053.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "43.550mm" ver = "01" gw = "194" gh = "106"/>
</figure>
</s2>
<c-change/>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Install bevel pinion dummy, rear taper roller bearing (1) and special tools to transfer output retainer (2).
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L3C028">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09922-76140">
09922–76140
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L3C029">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09922-76420">
09922–76420
</s-number>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L3C030">
<s-part>
(C)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09922-76340">
09922–76340
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L3C031">
<s-part>
(D)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09922-76150">
09922–76150
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
This installation requires no spacer or oil seal.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A330029.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "80.192mm" ver = "01" gw = "191" gh = "211"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "3.150in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
“a”:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Pinion dummy height 40 mm (1.575 in.)
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
“b”:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Height from retainer installation face to top surface of pinion dummy
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
“c”:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Distance from retainer installation face to end face of bearing race
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s2>
<c-change/>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Tighten bevel pinion nut (special tool) so that specified bearing preload is obtained.
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<ptxt>
Before taking measurement, turn bevel pinion 15 rotations or more by hand in order to settle bearings in carrier.
</ptxt>
</attention3>
<spec>
<title>
Rotational torque of bevel pinion (Bearing preload)
</title>
<ptxt>
0.50 – 1.30 N&#183;m (0.05 – 0.13 kgf-m, 0.35 – 0.95 lbf-ft)
</ptxt>
</spec>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A330030.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "40.232mm" ver = "01" gw = "103" gh = "98"/>
</figure>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Measure height “b” in figure by using vernier caliper.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Calculate “c” by using measured value.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "5" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.866in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "0.157in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "0.748in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "0.157in"/>
<colspec colnum = "5" colname = "5" colwidth = "1.181in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
Distance “c”
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "0" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
=
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "0" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
Height “b”
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "0" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
–
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "5" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
Height “a” 40 mm (1.575 in.)
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A330031.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "78.564mm" ver = "01" gw = "175" gh = "206"/>
</figure>
</s2>
<c-change/>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Obtain adjusting shim thickness by the following equation.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "7" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.857in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "0.157in"/>
<colspec colnum = "3" colname = "3" colwidth = "0.653in"/>
<colspec colnum = "4" colname = "4" colwidth = "0.157in"/>
<colspec colnum = "5" colname = "5" colwidth = "0.695in"/>
<colspec colnum = "6" colname = "6" colwidth = "0.157in"/>
<colspec colnum = "7" colname = "7" colwidth = "0.771in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" morerows = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
Necessary shim thickness “f”
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" morerows = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "0" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
=
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "3" morerows = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "0" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
Distance “c”
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "4" morerows = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "0" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
+
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "5" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "0" border-left = "0" border-right = "0" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
Distance “d”
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "6" morerows = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "0" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
–
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "7" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "0" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
Distance “e” 
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "5" border-top = "0" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "0" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
74.0 mm (2.913 in.)
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "7" border-top = "0" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "middle" align = "center">
<ptxt>
105.95 mm (4.171 in.)
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I5RW0A330037.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "61.260mm" ver = "01" gw = "174" gh = "157"/>
<callout>
<table frame = "all" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<tgroup cols = "2" colsep = "1" rowsep = "1">
<colspec colnum = "1" colname = "1" colwidth = "0.315in"/>
<colspec colnum = "2" colname = "2" colwidth = "3.150in"/>
<tbody>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
“d”:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Pinion shaft mounting distance 74.0 mm (2.913 in.)
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "1">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
“e”:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Distance from end face of left case to axis of reduction driven gear 105.95 mm (4.171 in.)
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
<row rowsep = "0">
<entry colname = "1" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "1" border-right = "0" valign = "top" align = "right">
<ptxt>
“f”:
</ptxt>
</entry>
<entry colname = "2" border-top = "1" border-bottom = "1" border-left = "0" border-right = "1" valign = "top" align = "left">
<ptxt>
Necessary shim thickness
</ptxt>
</entry>
</row>
</tbody>
</tgroup>
</table>
</callout>
</figure>
</s2>
<s2>
<ptxt>
Select a shim closest to the calculated value (necessary shim thickness) from among the available shims or combine shims to become closest to calculated value.
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
<emph etype = "bold">
For example:
</emph>
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Measure distance “b” is 73.95 mm (2.911 in.).
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
“c” = 73.95 mm (2.911 in.) – 40.0 mm (1.575 in.) = 33.95 mm (1.337 in.)
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
“f” = 33.95 mm (1.337 in.) + 74.0 mm (2.913 in.) – 105.95 mm (4.171 in.) = 2.0 mm (0.079 in.)
</ptxt>
<ptxt>
Calculated thickness of new shim = 2.0 mm (0.079 in.)
</ptxt>
<spec>
<title>
Available bevel pinion shim thickness
</title>
<ptxt>
0.30, 1.85, 1.88, 1.91, 1.94, 1.97, 2.00, 2.03, 2.06, 2.09, 2.12 and 2.15 mm (0.012, 0.073, 0.074, 0.075, 0.076, 0.078, 0.079, 0.080, 0.081, 0.082, 0.083 and 0.084 in.)
</ptxt>
</spec>
</s2>
</s1>
<c-change/>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Press-fit front outer race and rear outer race using special tool and hydraulic press.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L3C032">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09913-75520">
09913–75520
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L3C033">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09924-84510">
09924–84510
</s-number>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L3C034">
<s-part>
(C)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09941-34513">
09941–34513
</s-number>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A330032.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "34.659mm" ver = "01" gw = "159" gh = "82"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Press-fit pinion shaft front taper roller bearing (1) using special tool and hydraulic press.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L3C035">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09925-18011">
09925–18011
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "I5RW0A330039.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "46.310mm" ver = "01" gw = "64" gh = "115"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install bevel pinion (1) with pinion shaft spacer (2) to transfer output retainer (3).
</ptxt>
<attention2>
<ptxt>
Be sure to use new pinion shaft spacer.
</ptxt>
</attention2>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Apply oil to pinion shaft front taper bearing (4) and pinion shaft rear taper bearing (5).
</ptxt>
<materials>
<materialitem name = "SUZUKI gear oil (75W-85 / GL-5)" id = "M3C009" uid = "1277266418">
<m-part>
“A”
</m-part>
<m-desc>
Gear Oil
</m-desc>
<m-number>
99000–22B30
</m-number>
<m-name>
SUZUKI gear oil (75W-85 / GL-5)
</m-name>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</materialitem>
</materials>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Drive in pinion shaft rear taper roller bearing using special tool and tapping lightly with plastic hammer.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L3C036">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09924-07720">
09924–07720
</s-number>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</servicetoolitem>
<servicetoolitem id = "L3C037">
<s-part>
(B)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09913-85210">
09913–85210
</s-number>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A330033.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "44.459mm" ver = "01" gw = "171" gh = "110"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Apply grease to new oil seal lip.
</ptxt>
<materials>
<materialitem name = "SUZUKI Super Grease A" id = "M3C010" uid = "1126491901">
<m-part>
“A”
</m-part>
<m-desc>
Grease
</m-desc>
<m-number>
99000–25011
</m-number>
<m-name>
SUZUKI Super Grease A
</m-name>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</materialitem>
</materials>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Drive in oil seal (1) using special tool and hammer.
</ptxt>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L3C038">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09925-16510">
09925–16510
</s-number>
<ptxt>
</ptxt>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<spec>
<title>
Installation position of oil seal
</title>
<ptxt>
“a”: 16 – 17 mm (0.63 – 0.66 in.)
</ptxt>
</spec>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A330034.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "53.094mm" ver = "01" gw = "163" gh = "134"/>
</figure>
</s1>
<s1>
<ptxt>
Install transfer output flange (1) by tapping with plastic hammer and tighten transfer output flange nut gradually so as rotational torque of bevel pinion to be in specified value.
</ptxt>
<attention3>
<list1 type = "unordered">
<item>
<ptxt>
If rotational torque of bevel pinion exceeds specification given in the following, replace pinion shaft spacer and tighten flange nut.
</ptxt>
</item>
<item>
<ptxt>
Before taking measurement of rotational torque, rotate pinion over ten turns in advance.
</ptxt>
</item>
</list1>
</attention3>
<spec>
<title>
Bevel pinion bearing preload
</title>
<ptxt>
: 0.5 – 1.3 N&#183;m (0.05 – 0.13 kgf-m, 0.35 – 0.95 lbf-ft)
</ptxt>
</spec>
<servicetool>
<servicetoolitem id = "L3C039">
<s-part>
(A)
</s-part>
<s-number num = "09930-40113">
09930–40113
</s-number>
</servicetoolitem>
</servicetool>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A330035.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "50.374mm" ver = "01" gw = "139" gh = "126"/>
</figure>
<figure>
<graphic graphicname = "IAP70A330036.swf" width = "88.000mm" height = "48.329mm" ver = "01" gw = "125" gh = "120"/>
<callout>
